channel.title: ๖ۣۜNRS3server 667
channel.description:
[center][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/B4an9.png[/img]
[size=10pt]Acdodo and Sam Akin You wish i made this for you but you guys are nothing but pricks
The time has finally come and the source is finally released you guys have hassled me alot for this source and i am finally done enough to release this to the public although there is still lots more i would love to release with this source sadle i can not since i have exams and i will be gone on vacation rite after it so i will release more later[/size]
Here are some features
[size=14pt][b][u]Recent Updates:[/u][/b][/size] Finished PACKING zammy and arma not done hp Fixed trading Fixed Castle Wars 100% Clan wars Soul Wars is now in construction 40% Dominion Tower Complete partially
[size=12pt][u][b]Features:[/b][/u][/size] - Switching is near perfect - All Spellbooks are accessible via Commands and altars - Storm of Armadyl, New boots, and more. - Armours such as Torva, Barrows, and PvP Armour Degrade when in use and when they are dropped in PvP - Auras are all complete except for Salvation and Corruption bonuses work wings are glitched
(Bosses) - King Black Dragon with all attacks and effects - Tormented Demons with all 3 switches - Full Nex with all 4 stages (Flawless) - 85% Godwars - Corporeal beast with Impact hits and all correct attacks - Frost dragons - Dominion Tower - Barrows{prizes glitchy still} & More...
Pvp/PK/PVM/Combat - Near Perfect combat, 99.9% flawless - Switching better than RS - Full Summoning!! - Armour set effects all added! - Degrading Pvp Armours - Storm Of Armadyl Spell - Flawless Prayer system (Normal/Ancient Prayers/Lunar)
Random Stuff: - All special attacks working properly for Most Weapons! - Quick Chat 100% - music everyone knows that - custom maps - donorzones staffzones and more
Armours/Bosses: - All new 711 armours obv we all know - Bosses are upgraded to new looks - Jad waves maxed out to 65 - Armours are almost all update to date with bonuses and stats - Each armour that need requirements on RS is same on here now - Quests are partially made
Home/Shops [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/30l29p4.png[/img] SkillCape shop is now corresponding with the skills you have acheived [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/2u5z9g1.png[/img] Armours are almost all up to date with bonuses [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/9zlopx.png[/img] Grand Exchange is now Working still a few bugs but works well and all items almost added [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/fnqy6w.png[/img] Grand exchange was taken out due to being extremely laggy and to many bugs
[img]http://i47.tinypic.com/ulhfm.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/353cizk.png[/img] [img]http://i46.tinypic.com/351buwp.png[/img] [img]http://i48.tinypic.com/5vdco0.png[/img] [img]http://i47.tinypic.com/14x1ox0.png[/img]
[b]Crystal to save your game in locations and teleporting[/b] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2ldatzr.png[/img] [b]duel arena with proper interfaces[/b] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2itjukh.png[/img] [b]PolyPore Working 100%[/b] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/fu7yj4.png[/img] [b]Dominion Tower with all modes[/b] [IMG]http://i46.tinypic.com/207lug7.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2zz01v9.png[/img] [b]Glacors[/b] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/muzwcz.jpg[/img] [b]Jadinko's[/b] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/348mw5y.png[/img] [b]New Player logg interfaces[/b] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/72u4hx.png[/img] [b]Gnome Agility Course[/b] [IMG]http://i45.tinypic.com/20uub9c.png[/img]
[b]Final Update Just dicing[/b] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/1ex7k9.png[/img] [IMG]http://i47.tinypic.com/9i5ogw.png[/img]
[size=14pt]I GIVE NO PERMISSION FOR THIS TO BE RELEASED ANYWHERE ELSE IF I SO DECIDE TO RELEASE THIS ELSE WHERE I WILL DO IT
THERE IS NO MORE ANTI LEECH ON IT AND BECAUSE SOME NOOB RE-RELEASED THIS SOURCE WITHOUT MY PERMISSION AND ALSO BECAUSE THERE IS NO MORE ANTI LEECH I WILL NOT BE RELEASING A V2[/size]
